Lighting Panel Operator 🟢
.
We work alongside the GMC (Ground Movement Controller) and control the lighting for all taxiways leading up to the runway strip. It’s a complex job as you can’t let any aircraft come into conflict with eachother, either by pushing back into the path of an aircraft that’s taxiing, or two aircraft coming head-to-head on the taxiway (a big No-No). 
.
Gatwick’s taxiway network is complex which makes the job very tricky. Alongside this we operate the vehicle crossings, send METARs, liaise with Airfield Ops and Stand Planning with all sorts of issues. We are essentially the second pair of eyes and ears for the GMC. It’s high pressure but the job satisfaction after a good session is immense! 
.

What is a clear chrome powder?

HONA's clear chrome pigment will give any coloured gel polish a high gloss glass finish. Perfect product for creating glazed doughnut / donut nails.

Treat this chrome powder completely the same as any other chrome.

What are the key features of this nail chrome

	* Solid state in compressed container
	* Non-toxic
	* Colourfast & fade Resistant
	* Non-bleed

How To Apply

Application using a non wipe top coat
1. Apply your chosen gel colour and cure
2. Apply 1 coat of non wipe top coat
3. Rub in the chrome powder
4. Dust off any excess chrome powder
5. Lightly buff around the free edge to remove excess powder and prevent chipping
6. Apply top coat of your choice
7. For a more durable finish repeat step 6.

【回家】

Southampton to Gatwick Airport，送本區街坊一家四口去機場，客人係斯里蘭卡人，移居英國後從事大學研究工作，今次係一家人返去家鄉渡假。過往我都服務過好多亞裔嘅街坊朋友，斯里蘭卡就係第一次。得知大家都係來自亞洲後，客人對於香港都好有興趣，因為佢都有留意幾年前英國媒體對香港嘅報導，而我當然都有把握機會盡力講解。

不過佢就話一直都未有機會到訪香港，但就好鐘意去鄰近嘅泰國，咁又係，相信「泰鐘意」呢一部分絕對係無國界🤣
